quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  61,10,“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Kodi ndikudziwitseni malonda amene angakupulumutseni ku chilango chowawa
  61,11,"“Muzimkhulupirira Allah ndi Mtumiki Wake; ndipo muzichita Jihâd pa njira ya Allah ndi chuma chanu, ndi matupi anu. Zimenezo nzabwino kwa inu ngati muli odziwa"
  61,12,"“Akukhululukirani machimo anu ndipo akulowetsani m’minda momwe mitsinje ikuyenda pansi pake, ndiponso (adzakupatsani) mokhala mwabwino ku minda yamuyaya. Kumeneko ndiko kupambana kwakukulu"
  61,13,“Ndizina zomwe mukuzifuna. Thandizo (lonse) lichokera kwa Allah ndi kugonjetsa kumene kuli pafupi; ndipo auze nkhani yabwino okhulupirira
  61,14,"“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Khalani othangata (kufalitsa chipembedzo cha) Allah (pamene Mtumiki akukuitanani kuti mumthangate) monga momwe adanenera Isa (Yesu) mwana wa Mariya powauza otsatira ake: “Ndani adzandithangata pa ntchito ya Allah (yofalitsa chipembedzo Chake)? Otsatira ake adanena: “Ife ndife othangata (kufalitsa chipembedzo cha) Allah.” Choncho gulu lina la ana a Israyeli lidakhululupirira, ndipo gulu lina silidakhululupirire, tero tidawapatsa mphamvu amene adakhulupirira pa adani awo, ndipo adali opambana"